item.description: Ethereum Mining Calculator Use this mining calculator to figure out your profitability for your mining rig(s). You will want to plug in the following 4 values to the calculator below based on your planned setup. You can leave the other prepopulated values as is. Hashing Power - The total amount of compute power for your rig. Normally measured in MH/s. (e.g. An nVidia 1070 GTX card normally gets around 26.
